      "date": "2011-11-15 05:02:02.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Fails\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/0ea40852-0f42-11e1-9051-52540025f9af).  Ran 15 tests.  1 tests failed: replay-dual.",
