      "date": "2011-11-21 19:24:36.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(3 inline comments)\n\nDo you know what distro \"bool\" was added for userspace?  I'm reluctant to commit this without knowing, since this is the first use of the \"bool\" type in the Lustre code.\n\nThis patch didn't build due to the issues over the weekend, so I've resubmitted it.  That will tell if the limited number of distros we build on will allow this, but it would be good to know which older distros this would break on.",
