      "date": "2011-11-28 08:09:04.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 4: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS Linux release/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/1782b522-1997-11e1-bdf8-52540025f9af).  Ran 13 tests.  No failures.",
